			&nbsp;<BR>

			penemo performs various functions such as ping checks, 
			http requests (with the optional feature of doing 
			a pattern match on the fetched URL), and, of course,
			it can poll snmp agents for related information. 
			Currently it only really supports the UCD-SNMP agent 
			daemon and not really any proprietary MIBs. Though 
			adding specifications for new MIB isn't a very 
			difficult task and the concept is modular in design.<BR>

